Most likely outcome

At this point I suspect one of two things:

1. mpm_shell.py will work once PYTHONPATH is fixed
2. uhd_usrp_probe is loading a mismatched libuhd or mixed install on the host

Your next three outputs should settle that:

* find /workspace/uhd -name 'mprpc*'
* ldd "$(which uhd_usrp_probe)" | grep libuhd
* the result of mpm_shell.py after setting PYTHONPATH
